        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
          "markdown": "\u2022 Fixed the dock's icon list keeping its old, narrower frame after the dock itself expanded to full width",
          "useSpacing": false
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
          "markdown": "\u2022 This mismatch was making the icon row (most visible entering the App Library) drift and scroll horizontally on its own",
          "useSpacing": false
        },
        {
          "class": "DepictionMarkdownTextView",
          "markdown": "\u2022 The icon list now snaps to the dock's full bounds and locks out scrolling if it's backed by a scroll view",
